<div class="home-page">
  <section class="hero-section">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1 class="hero-title">NestBB에 오신 것을 환영합니다</h1>
      <p class="hero-description">
        It is a modern bulletin board system built based on <b>handlebar + NestJS and MongoDB</b><br/>
        Experience a fast, safe(?), and scalable community platform
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/posts" class="btn-secondary-large">게시판 보기</a>
        <a href="/posts/write" class="btn-secondary-large">글 작성하기</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-number">1,234</div>
        <div class="stat-label">총 게시글</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-number">5,678</div>
        <div class="stat-label">총 댓글</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-number">892</div>
        <div class="stat-label">활성 사용자</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="features-section">
    <h2 class="section-heading">주요 기능</h2>
    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">⚡</div>
        <h3 class="feature-title">빠른 성능</h3>
        <p class="feature-description">NestJS 기반의 최적화된 서버 사이드 렌더링으로 빠른 페이지 로딩을 제공합니다.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🔒</div>
        <h3 class="feature-title">안전한 보안</h3>
        <p class="feature-description">TypeScript의 타입 안정성과 검증된 보안 프레임워크로 데이터를 안전하게 보호합니다.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🎨</div>
        <h3 class="feature-title">모던한 디자인</h3>
        <p class="feature-description">깔끔하고 직관적인 UI/UX로 누구나 쉽게 사용할 수 있습니다.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">📱</div>
        <h3 class="feature-title">반응형 레이아웃</h3>
        <p class="feature-description">모바일, 태블릿, 데스크톱 모든 기기에서 완벽하게 작동합니다.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">💬</div>
        <h3 class="feature-title">실시간 댓글</h3>
        <p class="feature-description">게시글마다 자유롭게 의견을 나누고 소통할 수 있습니다.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🔍</div>
        <h3 class="feature-title">강력한 검색</h3>
        <p class="feature-description">원하는 내용을 빠르게 찾을 수 있는 검색 기능을 제공합니다.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="recent-posts-section">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-heading">최근 게시글</h2>
      <a href="/posts" class="view-all-link">전체 보기 →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="recent-posts-grid">
      {{#each posts}}
        <article class="recent-post-card">
          <div class="post-badge">New</div>
          <h3 class="recent-post-title">{{this.title}}</h3>
          <p class="recent-post-excerpt">{{this.content}}</p>
          <div class="recent-post-meta">
            <span class="post-date">{{this.createdAt}}</span>
            <span class="post-stats">💬 {{this.comments.length}} · 👁 128</span>
          </div>
        </article>
      {{/each}}
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="cta-content">
      <h2 class="cta-title">지금 바로 시작하세요</h2>
      <p class="cta-description"><b>NestBB</b>와 함께 여러분의 이야기를 나누어보세요</p>
      <a href="/posts/write" class="btn-cta">첫 글 작성하기</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/home.css">